  "text": "In fact, the process of the data redistribution replies on the scheduling of the data movement of the input data. This schedule process could be very simple. For example, in a hash-based join [CITATION_1] , data tuples are assigned based on the hash values of their join keys. In the meantime, the process could be also very complex, e.g., track-join [CITATION_2] adopts a four phase schedule in its implementations.",
